						<p>Gift of a perpetual lamp to the deity Narasimha-āḷvār at Tiruvāṉaimalai in Kīḻ-iraṇiya-muṭṭam in Rājēntrachōḻa-vaḷanāḍu in Rājarāja-pāṇḍi-nāḍu by Tattaṉ Chēnti, a brāhamaṇa woman of Iṟaiyāṉaraichūr.</p>						

